Label: Radial_Offset_Adjustment
test: -9999 #Radial offset is in millimetre(mm) with +ve values actioning radial outward movement and -ve values actioning radial inward movement of the magnets.

Label: RobotTemp
test: 14.0000 #temperature (degrees C) the distortion code assumed the field would be observed at

Label: ObsTemp
test: 14.0000 #actual temperature (degrees C) it is going to be observed at

Label: Radial_Scale_factor
test: 1.0 #Radial scale factor is thermal coefficient of invar times temperature difference applied radially relative to the plate centre.
